{"tid":662369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"系統暴露私隱　司機專揀美女客","createTime":"2018-05-12T11:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T17:24:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52b1510bf7318480f44b8a8b4fdaf7d0ae3ed431","tid":662369,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180512/20388339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180512%2F20388339&d=QLLjAeUuz8vvragMMw%2FMP%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=b29aab90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180512%2F20388339&h=1ad38acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180512/20388339</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月12日 <br />\n<br />\n系統暴露私隱　司機專揀美女客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180512/large/12cb2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180512%2Flarge%2F12cb2p.jpg&h=3feff728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉振華犯案後棄車跳河，當局派員搜捕稱「活要見人，死要見屍」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n空姐被滴滴順風車主姦殺，事件已不再是普通的謀殺案，不少人發現滴滴順風車的安全隱憂。有內媒發現，滴滴司機能在司機乘客的互評系統得知乘客身材及樣貌，甚至有否走光，資料瞬即被其他司機觀看。順風車司機良莠不齊，單是深圳已超過3,000人有吸毒或重大刑事案前科。中國交通部昨炮轟：「網約車平台不顧乘客體驗，終將會轟然倒塌」。<br />\n<br />\n中國媒體《北京時間》發現，滴滴順風車的司機乘客互評系統問題嚴重，司機會評價女乘客「聲音甜美、身材好」，甚至留言「美女下車時絲襪容易走光的令人想入非非」、「膚白貌美大長腿，一個人怕不住」。這些資訊全部公開，包括其他滴滴司機在內，所有人能看，故乘客未上車，滴滴司機已經藉此挑選乘客，甚至知道乘客的樣貌身材。北京時間派女記者實試，一旦被評為「貌美」，數分鐘已吸引幾個男司機觀看。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深圳逾千司機曾吸毒<br />\n<br />\n據內媒不完全統計，最少有11宗涉及滴滴司機的強姦案。他們一般會套取女乘客的個人資料，判斷「是否容易佔便宜」，再伺機作案。<br />\n<br />\n官方曾經排查滴滴在內的五間順風車平台，單是深圳市便發現1,425名滴滴順風車司機有吸毒前科，有1661人有重大刑事犯罪前科。繼中共中央機關報《人民日報》前天要求滴滴堵塞漏洞外，交通運輸部亦批評，網約車平台不承擔社會責任，不顧乘客體驗，「終將會轟然倒塌」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n網民「捐錢」　盼疑兇提款洩行蹤<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n安倍「罕見禮遇」李克強　再共晉餐<br />\n<br />\n用戶4.5億　日定單2,500萬<br />\n<br />\n網民「捐錢」　盼疑兇提款洩行蹤<br />\n<br />\n滴滴司機涉姦殺空姐犯案後棄車跳河　警撈獲屍體待鑑定"},{"pid":"8efcb3642752eb57e1c765a516cf9f0b458f17d4","tid":662369,"uid":21052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"大陸野真係柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但已經預計係香港會合法先過Uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f06b178d1a4a84a8f3dc4dfa2fe152eec5c446","tid":662369,"uid":18772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"張圖條友好似鴨屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180512/large/12cb2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180512%2Flarge%2F12cb2p.jpg&h=7385597b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad098cfe476df78153a6a00485971a1ef68cfc9f","tid":662369,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"DiDi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港有啲的士都有"},{"pid":"50e1053d3ab9e2eacfa368eec4dbd3cdbe17b1a4","tid":662369,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad098cfe476df78153a6a00485971a1ef68cfc9f","tid":662369,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"DiDi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港有啲的士都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"應該用左個優惠就唔用啦<br />\n避稅大過天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}